    "description": "《僭越：无光之日》将带领玩家进入云林村，以第一人称视角给玩家带来一场充满悬疑的惊悚冒险。玩家需要躲避阴影中的恐怖怪物，收集每一条可能与家人有关的线索，孤独地挑战一个延续了六十年之久的邪教组织和束缚在这片土地上受诅咒的灵魂。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/763a28483f9ae5b0509e21f89681d33b.avif?t=1681788600\" width=616 height=352 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >80年代的乡村，传统与进步诡异的交织</h2>昏暗的光线、空旷的建筑、莫名的阴风以及从黑暗角落中传来的怪异响动，这座80年代的无人村庄无时无刻不在挑动着玩家脆弱的神经。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/b78a2f976495af84adcf03206c7895af.poster.avif?t=1681788600\" width=614 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/b78a2f976495af84adcf03206c7895af.webm?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/b78a2f976495af84adcf03206c7895af.mp4?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全方位的恐怖，带你进入一场神秘诡谲的谜团</h2>难以名状的怪物，隐藏在重重迷雾中的惨剧，为你带来战栗不安的惊悚氛围，唤醒你对未知的恐惧。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/fd85780be3b1e32acda510f6cfaa647f.poster.avif?t=1681788600\" width=614 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/fd85780be3b1e32acda510f6cfaa647f.webm?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/fd85780be3b1e32acda510f6cfaa647f.mp4?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想尽一切办法，活下去！</h2>荒村之中，危机四伏，你需要敏捷和果断，才能逃出生天。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/fdfcfc095b9736ebed85884f54ec82b6.poster.avif?t=1681788600\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/fdfcfc095b9736ebed85884f54ec82b6.webm?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/fdfcfc095b9736ebed85884f54ec82b6.mp4?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在这片神秘的黑暗中，隐藏着无数的秘密</h2>风格多样的特色机关谜题遍布地图，声音、光线、垃圾乃至恐怖的怪物都可能是解谜的关键，直面你的恐惧，找出真相和最后的出路吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/a9ba1173d0287d1621418f3042f40814.poster.avif?t=1681788600\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/a9ba1173d0287d1621418f3042f40814.webm?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155160/extras/a9ba1173d0287d1621418f3042f40814.mp4?t=1681788600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
